<h1 class="mb-3">Privacy at EasExpo</h1>
<p class="text-muted">We collect only the information required to deliver booking, payment, and management features across the EasExpo platform.</p>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">What we store</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Account information provided during registration (name, email, company details).</li>
    <li>Stall listings and booking history to coordinate availability.</li>
    <li>Payment references for reconciliation and reporting.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">How we use it</h2>
<p>Your information powers the dashboards, reports, and workflows required for smooth expo management. Sensitive payment operations can be delegated to secure gateways such as Razorpay or PayPal.</p>

<h2 class="h5 mt-4">Need help?</h2>
<p>Contact the EasExpo administrator to request changes or removal of your data.</p>
